    "text": [
        "Recently, owing to the rapid development of advanced technology, people have combined their daily life with the internet. As far as I am concerned, this trend can be a positive development as it can help break the geographical barrier as well as raise living standards.",
        "To begin with, using the internet allows people to build up a stronger connection with the world. As it seems difficult for people to meet foreigners because of the geographical barrier, using the internet may provide citizens with various platforms to chat with people from different countries. For example, the public can communicate with those who post similar interests on Instagram. Therefore, citizens may expose themselves to diverse cultures and traditions once they are encouraged to interact with others, despite their nationality, social status and age.",
        "Moreover, living standards can be enhanced by using the internet. Since citizens can only purchase indigenous goods in their local markets before, the variety of products may be limited. However, by introducing the internet, citizens can be encouraged to try some exotic products. For instance, people from Africa can also enjoy sushi from Japan. Therefore, people can benefit from the desirable outcome of globalization. The quality of life can also be increased since there are more choices being provided to the general public.",
        "In conclusion, it is undeniable that the internet plays an important role in gathering people together from different regions as well as spreading diverse cultures. Moreover, the internet can also help improve living standards by providing access to various products."
